       /*****************************************************************************************************************
    *    Method Name   :    fireRequestMap
    *    Description   :    Fires HTTP request and stores the response with SUCCESS/FAILURE
    *    Params        :    HttpRequest request
    *    Return Type   :    Map<String,String>
